Class GameError

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
java.lang.RuntimeException
GameError
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class GameError extends RuntimeException
Defines run-time errors that can be thrown during the execution of the game.
